google.description: In the wake of a series of suspicious deaths on the moors of Dark Peak, detectives Diane Fry and Ben Cooper struggle with a two-year-old unsolved case involving a secretive clan and the death of a young woman whose parents insist that she is still alive. Reprint.
google.title: Blind to the Bones
